{
  "stem": "19055.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So there was a gradual shifting and shifting to the right and more and more to radicalizing the country toward Nazism.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So when the Germans came in, not just there was no resistance, but there was an absolute cooperation in, in any way and anywhere by the police, by the gendarmerie, by the government.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans came in [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] March or April, April of 1944.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was less than 14.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I recall very, very clearly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that the Germans arrived to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they, they took over in a friendly manner with no resistance, as I say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on that day in the morning, somebody said the Germans came to town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we all went out then to see on the Main Street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They came with their motorcycles and the gondola and their black leather jackets and raincoats and, and helmets, just like we see today in the Second World War movies.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything was black and fearsome.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the, the captain, he got up with the motorcycle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he started to walk on Main Street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were watching him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was hitting his boots with his riding stick and then pointed to my friend's house, which was a villa on Main Street.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And his mother was my pediatrician.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He said this is going to be German headquarters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they had to move out immediately from that house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And from then on, the events rolled very rapidly after the Germans had arrived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Jews knew-- we, we all knew that something is coming, that it will be terrible.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we didn't know what exactly and how this will happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
